; Coverage for value.cc amount divided by single-amount balance
; When display_total is a balance with a single commodity, dividing an amount
; by it triggers the balance simplification path in operator/=

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/02 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg Expenses --format "%(amount / display_total)\n"
$1.00
$0.50
end test
